data.description: Looking for the perfect home? Welcome to 1763 Rowland Ave. Take a look at this spacious Midcentury 4bd, 2.5 ba, 2-story home in the heart of Camarillo. Completely re-plumbed, newer roof, newer heater, windows and sliding glass doors are just some of the upgraded amenities. The large living area is wonderful for entertaining along with a formal dining room. A generous size family room is great for relaxing or just enjoying a warm cozy fire. The spacious kitchen offers ample cabinet space, dual ovens and eat-in-area. If a large backyard is what you are looking for, then you will enjoy this wonderful backyard retreat with mature orange and lemon trees. You will love the 8000 sqft lot with vinyl fencing. All the bedrooms are upstairs- 3 with wonderful views of the backyard. This lovely home offers opportunities to bring your own touch and style. Come take a look!
